In crafting CrunchyPix, I harnessed cutting-edge technologies, utilizing Next.js (v14) and TypeScript as primary tools. React provided the flexibility and robustness required to bring the vision to life. To ensure a seamless user experience worldwide, I integrated i18n and employed custom language translation components. Using Redux for state management, I handled intricate details such as language preferences, custom cursor interactions, and device responsiveness. Enchanting animation transitions, crafted with motion.div and meticulously developed custom variants, breathe life into CrunchyPix. Each subpage, whether showcasing products or services, is dynamically generated, offering a responsive environment.
&nbsp;
My commitment extends to using version control and collaboration tools like GitHub, where I store and manage project files. Dependabot, CodeQL, and Vercel are additional tools enhancing the development workflow. Feel free to access the project's source code on GitHub for a more detailed exploration.
